metadata.name: Multidimensional Woman
metadata.description:
The artwork portrays a woman existing in a five-dimensional world, with a spectrum of vivid colors enveloping her being. Behind her, the viewer can glimpse other universes beyond our own, suggesting a vast and limitless cosmic expanse. The artwork invites contemplation on the nature of reality, perception, and the interconnectedness of all things. It speaks to the human desire for exploration and discovery, and the pursuit of knowledge beyond what we currently understand.

Edition: 1 x 1
